Package camzup.core

Interface ISpatial3

All Known Implementing Classes:
CurveEntity3, Entity3, ImageEntity3, MeshEntity3, TextEntity3
public interface ISpatial3
Maintains consistent behavior for 3D animated objects with transforms.

  • Method Summary

    ISpatial3 moveBy​(Vec3 dir)
